  "hash_before": "6f9510bf552fb439beb440d602a39965cabcbb76b251d024a5dd1289d6cb735c",
  "heading_path": "光的衍射 / 单缝的夫琅禾费衍射",
  "intensity": "STRUCTURAL",
  "line_count": 121,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02547:3da3706c8411]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02548:ff2eb9e78880]]{figure}[htbp]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02549:444090bde130]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02550:c0439b87de4e]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02551:a95360f059e6]]{单缝的夫琅禾费衍射示意图}\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02552:06b3847e1b6f]]{figure}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02553:c285f6b40200]] \n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02554:c46e8799d850]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02555:ff2eb9e78880]]{figure}[htbp]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02556:444090bde130]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02557:0fa479c29845]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02558:a95360f059e6]]{明暗纹位置与宽度辅助图}\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02559:06b3847e1b6f]]{figure}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02560:3ea97b8d36ad]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02561:956f38899057]]\n\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02562:6203e55ca009]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02563:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n小角近似下，\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02564:5fddda0b1764]]\n先把 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02565:b06e9eb4fb6b]] 点对应的最大光程差写成波长的倍数：\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02566:10aaa3e48b97]]\n其中 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02567:d59fc13dc350]]。单缝明纹近似条件为\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02568:35d0024dcd38]]\n所以 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02569:b06e9eb4fb6b]] 点是第 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02570:9a0a01239ac9]] 级明纹。此时[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02571:02e0f372bfa3]]，每个半波带对应光程差 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02572:177aba1e82bb]]，故单缝可分成 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02573:9dc64f47b907]] 个半波带。若缝宽增加一倍，观察点 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02574:b06e9eb4fb6b]] 不动，则 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02575:2182836b0dd3]] 不变，而\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02576:1fe2ee6c6acb]]\n这满足单缝暗纹条件 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02577:9d3fdb5c7321]]，且 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02578:afe6acd7ffb2]]，所以 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02579:b06e9eb4fb6b]] 点变为第 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02580:9dc64f47b907]] 级暗纹。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02581:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02582:f8bef20a677e]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02583:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n同一装置中，单缝宽度 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02584:5220707bcc6c]] 和透镜焦距 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02585:a867d5ad6508]] 不变，中央明纹宽度只随波长成正比：\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02586:84a8869f8261]] \n蓝紫光波长比钠黄光短，算出的中央明纹也更窄，这和衍射图样随波长缩小的判断一致。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02587:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02588:81dd4f59364b]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02589:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02590:9c563fe2618b]] \n题目给的是两侧第三级暗纹之间的全距离，故单侧 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02591:ee84b2ac2bf6]]，于是\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02592:668d410103e7]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02593:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n",
  "mode": "REWRITE",
